div.div: Ju Seo-Cheon, a man who survives the age of war through sheer luck and becomes the elder of the Hwasan faction, only to live a life full of regrets and doubts. As he lies on his death bed, waiting for the inevitable, he is returned to the past...

After transmigrating, Ye Xuan chanced upon the Devouring System. Not only could he devour everything, he could also exchange things for bloodlines, martial arts, divine weapons, medicinal pills, and all sorts of treasures… A ridiculously broken system! “Don’t you dare mess with me. Want to try me? I’ll swallow that precious divine sword of yours!” (Source: Manga Bilibili, translated)
